## Strategic Guidance Summary

**Overall Workload Characterization:**
- TPC-H SF10 is a parallel analytical workload with 59M-60M row tables
- GenDB is competitive on Q1 (48ms) but underperforming on Q3 (386ms vs 77-84ms DuckDB) and Q6 (29.3ms vs 19ms DuckDB)
